<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Monterey Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in the mid-eighties, the community in Monterey Park takes the architectural inspiration from a Californian theme and is represented by the Ward 5 Councilor in the Calgary City Council. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Named after the city of Monterey Park in California, the Monterey Park is the residential neighborhood located in the North East side of Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">A majority of the homes for sale in Monterey Park comprise single-family detached and attached units with a few low-rise buildings offering apartments and condos as well. The average price of a listing in Monterey Park is on the lines of $390,000.</p>
        </div>
